Q-апплеты — это набор небольших и быстрых вспомогательных утилит системы Portage, написанных на C. В этом руководстве охватываются некоторые общие применения этих вспомогательных утилит, которые находятся в пакете {{Package|app-portage/portage-utils}}.

The {{Package|app-portage/portage-utils}} package is a collection of very fast utilities written in C, which are meant to offer a faster but more limited alternative to their {{Package|app-portage/gentoolkit}} counterparts. Please note that q applets are not meant to replace [[Gentoolkit|gentoolkit]]. The utilities may be much more efficient than the equivalent ones from [[Gentoolkit|gentoolkit]] and might be better suited to be used in scripts that need to call Portage repeatedly, but they ''do not'' offer the same functionality. q applets do not consider eclasses and do not provide tools like {{c|revdep-rebuild}} or {{c|glsa-check}}. 

